        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "eyebrow": "Our story",
        "heading_line_1": "Made with love,",
        "heading_line_2": "every single time",
        "intro_text": "<p>Hi, I'm Sarv - and every product you order from this shop is made personally by me, right here in Fuquay Varina, NC. Not by a factory. Not drop-shipped. By me, at my workstation, thinking about the person who's going to receive it.</p>",
        "story_title": "It started with my daughter",
        "story_body": "<p>My crafting journey began the way the best things do - out of love. As a mom, I found myself making everything my daughter asked for. Birthday decorations, school event crafts, little gifts that would make her eyes light up. Every project was a chance to create a special moment for her.</p><p>As she grew up and needed me a little less, I found myself with time on my hands and a heart full of creativity. So I kept going - learning new techniques, trying new materials, making things for friends and family. What started as a way to stay busy became something I genuinely couldn't stop doing.</p>",
        "highlight_quote": "\"I realized that what I was making for my daughter - that feeling of something made specifically for you - was something everyone deserved.\"",
        "story_footer": "<p>In 2024, Sarv's Arts and Crafts became official. But the way I work hasn't changed at all. Every order still gets the same care I put into the things I made for my little girl.</p>",
        "values_title": "What makes us different",
        "values_intro": "<p>Every single item at Sarv's Arts and Crafts is made in-house, by me - never drop-shipped. Your mug, your shirt, your laser-engraved keepsake - I make it, I check it, and I ship it. No warehouse, no middleman, no guessing.</p><p>What I hear most from customers is that they appreciate three things: the quality of what arrives, how quickly it gets to them, and that when they reach out - I actually respond. Fast. Those aren't happy accidents - they're what I've built this business around from day one.</p><p>From custom apparel and drinkware to laser-engraved gifts, every technique I offer is something I've personally mastered. If I can't do it well, I don't offer it.</p>",
        "family_title": "A little about our family",
        "family_body": "<p>I live with my husband, my now 10-year-old daughter (the original inspiration for all of this!), and our sweet dog. Fuquay Varina is home, and many of our local customers have become familiar faces I genuinely look forward to hearing from.</p><p>Whether you're ordering a single mug as a birthday gift or 50 shirts for your team - every order gets my full attention. That's a promise I've kept since day one and one I intend to keep.</p>",
        "cta_copy": "<p>Have a question about an order, a custom idea, or just want to say hello? I'd love to hear from you.</p>",
        "contact_email": "info@sarvsartsandcrafts.com",
